text:
According to the [API doc](http://docs.marklogic.com/jsdoc/valuesBuilder.BuiltQuery.html#where), the where clause takes a queryBuilder.query. With that in mind, you should be able to do something like this (not tested):

    var marklogic = require('marklogic');
    var vb = marklogic.valuesBuilder;
    var qb = marklogic.queryBuilder;
    vb
      .fromIndexes()
      .where(qb.value('month', 'November'))
